entries.femaleVariant: Brucie-baby! Was starting to think we'd never get ya outta that dump.
It's 'cause of people like you that camp even exists! I saw you 'hind the wheel... How much they payin' you, huh?!
Enough for me to buy for your ticket outta here! You can thank me later. Right now we gotta get moving.
Oh, and V! If you ever plan on quittin' Night City... careful 'round the borders. Accidents have a way of turnin' fatal.
